        4/24/2017
    

I've been coming to get my haircut here for a little over a year and Todd never fails to make me look my absolute best.  I receive frequent compliments on my hair from strangers and I've referred several friends here as well.  Todd takes great pride in his work and is very meticulous and consistent.  I always walk out of here feeling great and knowing I look good.The shop is very clean and stylish.  I love the decor and music.  It really feels like a more classical barbershop. Todd keeps a supply of top-notch, hand-picked products in stock.  I've switched over to using what he carries and I've never looked back.  I'm also thoroughly impressed at Todd's desire to improve his craft.  He goes to trade shows all over the world to learn new techniques and sample the latest products.  It definitely shows in the quality of his haircuts too.  You will not be disappointed at R Todd Fisher!!




