        4/16/2017
    

I've been getting my hair cut by Todd for over five years now, across three different locations. My cut is fairly simple, but has some "challenge" points that Todd is able to navigate with great skill. I always come out of his shop looking my best and feeling like I've had a great experience. The new storefront on Mueller Blvd. is one of the nicest barber shops I've ever seen. Great music, complimentary drinks and classic styling enhance the overall experience. I always look forward to my monthly appointments with Todd (for a cut) and Rudy (for a shave and beard trim); these are my "spa days" and a great way to step back from life's daily stresses and just relax for a couple hours. Easy online scheduling is just an added benefit, but be sure to book early as Todd's schedule fills up quickly, especially if you're looking for a weekend appointment.




