        4/21/2017
    

Todd is hands down the BEST barber I have ever been too. I was in the military for seven years and had to get weekly haircuts - so I've seen my fair share of barbers. I love that he takes pride in his work, is extremely detail orientated, doesn't rush, and is great to talk too. I've tried other barbers in Austin, and the quality of service Todd provides is second to none. Even when he has a busy day, he doesn't try to get me in and out as quick as he can. Previous barbers did this several times which led to a horrible cut. I don't have to worry about this with Todd. The compliments I routinely receive from friends and colleagues demonstrate that Todd consistently provides a great haircut. He knows what looks good. Trust him and you won't be disappointed!!




