        5/22/2017
    

Todd is the man. After moving back to Austin, it took me a while to find the right barber and luckily the best one in town had just set up shop around the corner from my house. The place is immaculate - definitely the style that I'd want to have in my own house. And he always has good music on. Character-wise, I'm not sure why some people have said he's an a-hole. Is he the most affable person in the world? Probably not. But he's hilarious, and you just have to get him started. One time he and I rescued some baby birds that were separated from their mother and trying to cross a busy street in front of his shop. Would an a-hole do that? I've been going every month for the last two years, and I hope that he renews his lease so that I can keep going there for many years to come.




