        4/15/2017
    

Todd has been my barber for the past year.Haircuts before Todd were obligations. The lack of consistency and attention to detail always bothered me, even in top dollar premier shops.Frustrated, I decided to see if Todd could help. I expressed what I wanted, and Todd actively listened. He offered valuable feedback, checked my understanding, and proceeded to give me the best haircut I've ever experienced. The attention to detail is unparalleled. Every experience afterward has remained top-notch. I now anticipate appointments with Todd.Todd's personable and very genuine. And on days when I'm feeling less conversational, Todd understands, which I greatly appreciate. The complementary trim service between appointments is a great addition, and keeps me looking sharp between cuts.Administratively, the online scheduling system is convenient and user friendly. If something comes up that needs attention beyond the app, Todd is quick to respond.




