        4/17/2017
    

Todd is a really fantastic barber with excellent taste, a discerning eye and an innate ability to provide a very clean, sharp and symmetrical cut. I went in for a haircut last year after finding him through Yelp and found my new barber. Each of the 7-10 cuts he has provided have been fantastic and very high-quality. He can improve any head of hair and style, but he is probably best know for haircuts for gentlemen, cuts that will make a suit or business casual look really pop, but still look good with bed-head and gym clothes too. The shop is super clean and very comfortable, and the music is usually dialed-in to awesome American soul and jazz tracks that are several layers more interesting than the junk-food pop that permeates many places.If you're considering giving him a try, don't hesitate. He gives the best men's cut in Austin I've found in two decades of living here.




